---
title: Mexican Spiced Fish & Kumara Fries with Charred Corn Salsa & Smokey Aioli
description: Mexican-spiced fish never fails to satisfy! Homemade salsa with warm charred corn and tomato tops a delicious spice coated fish fillet. Our side of easy kumara fries are the perfect accompaniment to this tasty dinner.
